cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.RO 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D motion capture of multiple people. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects, as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO) applications.
